payload.sql:
SELECT t.oid, t.typname
FROM pg_type as t
WHERE t.typname IN ('int2', 'int4', 'int8', 'oid', 'float4', 'float8', 'numeric', 'bool', 'timestamp', 'timestamptz')
payload.name: SCHEMA

payload.sql:
SELECT t.oid, t.typname, t.typelem, t.typdelim, t.typinput, r.rngsubtype, t.typtype, t.typbasetype
FROM pg_type as t
LEFT JOIN pg_range as r ON oid = rngtypid
WHERE
  t.typname IN ('int2', 'int4', 'int8', 'oid', 'float4', 'float8', 'text', 'varchar', 'char', 'name', 'bpchar', 'bool', 'bit', 'varbit', 'date', 'money', 'bytea', 'point', 'hstore', 'json', 'jsonb', 'cidr', 'inet', 'uuid', 'xml', 'tsvector', 'macaddr', 'citext', 'ltree', 'line', 'lseg', 'box', 'path', 'polygon', 'circle', 'time', 'timestamp', 'timestamptz', 'numeric', 'interval', 'cube', 'vector')
payload.name: SCHEMA

payload.sql:
